ute city\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"all basic necessities\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"a short walk or bike ride\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is been opposition from climate-skeptical people, the automotive lobby, and drivers in particular,\\\" Moreno said.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opposition\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"climate-skeptical people\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the automotive lobby\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"Moreno\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But this is no longer the time for cars, and we need to fight against them for a low-carbon future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"a low-carbon future\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That fight has made it to the U.S., but without much success.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That fight\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"much success\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some cities have embraced bike lanes and strengthened public transportation infrastructure, cars haveshown few signs of releasing their gripon U.S. transportation.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some cities\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"bike lanes\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"public transportation infrastructure\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"cars\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"few signs\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\